downloadDescription: A detailed matrix of supported Lync features comparing Lync Server 2013 with Lync Hoster Pack and Lync Online (Office 365).
detailsSection: A detailed matrix of supported Lync features comparing Lync Server 2013 with Lync Hoster Pack and Lync Online (Office 365).
systemRequirementsSection: • One file is a Microsoft Excel document. Users who do not have Microsoft Excel can view this document through the downloadable Excel Viewer.
installInstructionSection:
1. Click the Download button on this page to start the download, or choose a different language from the drop-down list and click Go.
  2. Do one of the following:
    • To start the installation immediately, click Open or Run this program from its current location.
    • To copy the download to your computer for installation at a later time, click Save or Save this program to disk.
